snippet.title: EverQuest: Empires of Kunark [Official Trailer]
snippet.description:
Empires of Kunark is now available NOW at https://bit.ly/EQ-EoK

Join us for Empires of Kunark, the 23rd EverQuest expansion, that has new zones, must-have in-game items, and adds the new Familiar Ring Key feature to the game!

Make haste and return to Kunark and choose your side in the coming turmoil. Tsaph Katta has rebuilt the capital of the Combine Empire in the treacherous lands of Kunark, and now focuses on uniting the races of Norrath – but not all are ready to bend to the will of the Combine Empire. Will a unified Norrath prevail or will the Combine's arrival lead to a war of catastrophic proportions?

Want to play EverQuest, the game that defined the MMORPG genre, for FREE? https://www.everquest.com/register

Subscribe!  http://ow.ly/fwV93097swI 
Play EverQuest for free: https://www.everquest.com/register
